{"tid":939615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣善信欲放生百隻巴西龜 險釀生態浩劫　","createTime":"2018-12-13T09:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T09:17:16.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10939309adfc70e6c63bb5a0a1deb073e664f3ea","tid":939615,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181213/_2018121315501399711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181213%2F_2018121315501399711.jpg&h=d136d1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有信徒自行攜帶逾百隻巴西幼龜，並準備到附近的溪流進行放生祈福。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n苗栗縣通霄鎮一間宮廟於上周六(8日)舉辦進香活動，誰料有來自台中的信徒，竟自行攜帶逾百隻巴西幼龜，並準備到附近的溪流進行放生祈福。當地民眾隨即報警，經勸說後，成功阻止這場生態浩劫。<br />\n<br />\n事後，宮廟人員指，他們從未辦理放生活動，當天是來進香的信徒，自行規劃的放生祈福，亦對他們放生的物種毫不知情。其後，相關事件及相片被轉發到Facebook，不少網友批評他們的舉動破壞大自然環境，部分人更指他們「造孽」，以及「應罰錢，影響生態」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/887200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F887200&d=Yhgvx6Hx6v2F34brKocgRbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=8da1d0d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F887200&h=90edca99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/887200</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}